<br>
Its obvious Mythic doesnt want to discuss our defense, so how about something more along the lines of group utility defense.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Suggestions</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Armor Factor Chant<br>
Ablative Armor Chant<br>
Pbae Snare Chant<br>
Determination Chant(ala Sorcerors)<br>
<br>
Offensive<br>
<br>
Its obvious Mythic deems our offensive abilites to be agreeable so perhaps focus on offensive group utility chants.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Suggestions</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
DPS+Haste Chant(20%DPS+20Haste) @highest Levels<br>
Equal Part (7.0dps Damage Shield/Damage Add)<br>
<br>
<br>
Realm Ability Review<br>
<br>
We all know FoTG is the worst ability ever...now officially proven to be &lt;7.0 dps(46 BS Damage add)...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Suggestions</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Increase FoTG substantially make it worth spending 14points on. DPS Damage add should be around 25-30+DPS, for a 14point RA with a 30minute reuse timer.<br>
<br>
